    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/mitchelton" style="color:#c4912a;">Mitchelton</a>, <a href="/suburbs/stafford" style="color:#c4912a;">Stafford</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kedron" style="color:#c4912a;">Kedron</a>.</p>
